beat her somehow!

159
00:10:41,900 --> 00:10:44,800
There's never been anything 
I couldn't get before!

160
00:10:45,400 --> 00:10:48,700
I will definitely steal victory away from her!

161
00:10:49,500 --> 00:10:52,730
