It's Inokuma Yawara!

181
00:12:13,400 --> 00:12:14,000
Oh shoot!

182
00:12:17,200 --> 00:12:18,700
Wait, wait!

183
00:12:43,700 --> 00:12:44,500
I'm sorry.

184
00:12:46,370 --> 00:12:50,000
